      <h2>General Information</h2>
      <p><strong>BharatNotes</strong> (<a href="https://bharatnotes.com">bharatnotes.com</a>) is a free educational resource created to help aspirants preparing for the UPSC Civil Services Examination (CSE). The content on this website is provided for <strong>general informational and educational purposes only</strong>.</p>

      <h2>Not Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>The content on BharatNotes does not constitute professional, legal, financial, or academic advice. While we strive for accuracy, the information should not be treated as a substitute for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Official UPSC notifications and syllabus documents</li>
        <li>Standard reference textbooks recommended for UPSC preparation</li>
        <li>Guidance from qualified mentors or coaching institutes</li>
        <li>Official government publications and gazettes</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Always cross-verify critical information — especially dates, constitutional provisions, statistics, and scheme details — with official sources before using it in your answers.</p>

