        <li>Statistics and data (economic figures, population data, etc.) are updated periodically and may become outdated</li>
        <li>Constitutional amendments and new legislation may alter previously accurate information</li>
        <li>PYQ analysis and subject weightage trends are based on available data and may vary by source</li>
      </ul>
      <p>BharatNotes is <strong>not liable</strong> for any errors, omissions, or outdated information. If you find an inaccuracy, please let us know via <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/epicbharat/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a> so we can correct it.</p>

